          "reviewBody": "Well they just adapted a new method to make a bit more money by simply making a mistake not once but twice and that is by changing the last date of the fee submission..\nIt's may 16 and today we got a message that the school is changing their last date of fee submission from 30th may to 16th of may i.e today , and if not paid till today they will add a fine that is 300 inr.\nI gave 2 stars just because of the teachers, the education system is good i appreciate it.\nThey made a new canteen where we get 1momo for about 10 inr and we don't even get it hot sometimes it's cold, feels like they cooked it yesterday and are selling it today",
          "publisher": {
