          "reviewBody": "I passed my higher secondary exams from the school. They were  my  best schooling days  ♥️. All my classmates were good and the senior and juniors too. All the teachers were good they were frank and caring, Father S.J Sebastian James used to be our principal and he took our classes too , his morals are stil valuable and will be too. The school has it's own beauty and infrastructure. The fest opus is a lit event to all. The open space and Greenery helps in concentration, and the play grounds are great too ,along with the stage hall. ♥️",
